Rangers knowledgeable in herbal lore are capable of foraging for healing
herbs while in the forest.  The herbs collected are capable of restoring the
health of the ranger himself, or a friend near by, at times healing even the
deadly plague.  
~
-1 0 HARA 'HARA KIRI'~
