The amazing reflexes and intuition of a battle-hardened samurai allow him
to switch from the opponent that he is currently fighting to a different one
with remarkable quickness.  A shuffle of the feet, a cunning feint, and a
sidestep later, the samurai places himself in front of a different opponent.

~
-1 0 'SECOND WEAPON'~
Only warriors, samurai and ninja are capable of learning this difficult
skill, as it requires great discipline in practicing and using.  If you are
wielding two weapons and your primary weapon is disarmed, you will
automatically switch the second weapon to your main hand.  While using a
second weapon, you can not hold an item or wear a shield.  
~
-1 0 'EXPLODE'~
Syntax: explode  {Ror{x  explode <target>

A samurai carries with him tiny jars of incendiary oil.  Casting a jar at
his foe, he focuses all of his mental energy on the oil, igniting it into
flame.  Fire erupts through the entire room, severely burning all of his
opponents.  Autopyrolisis is not an exact science, however, and as the
flames leap through the area, a samurai may also burn himself.  

The fire from explode is capable of destroying any burnable objects, wands,
scrolls, potions, staves and a few other things.
~
