~
-1 0 'CLEAVE'~
Syntax: cleave <victim>

While wielding an axe or sword, an anti-paladin is able to sneak up on an
unsuspecting opponent and attempt to cleave the victim's skull with his
weapon.  On a particularly powerful swing, there is a small chance that he
will cleave his opponent IN HALF, killing them instantly.  
~
-1 0 'VANISH'~
