A ninja carries smoke bombs with him, and when he desires, conjures one
forth and tosses it at the ground.  In the ensuing confusion, ever the
Master of Stealth, he vanishes.
 
Note: This teleports the ninja to a random room in the same area, it can
be used anytime, whether fighting or not.
~
-1 0 CALTROPS~
