right to live their life and go about their business as they see fit, as
long as you do not infringe on that same equal right of others.
  
{R*************************************************************************
**  {WThe areas that are defined as protected by the jurisdiction of     {R**
**  {Wthe Law are the entirety of Midgaard, New Thalos, Caerlon, and the {R**
