 Instead of having a Necromantic Dark-Elf dress is robes of black silk, with an ashen white face, taught to the touch and rough to the eye. Try to have him or her become a hauntingly beautiful Dark-Elf Necromancer who dresses in slightly vibrant colours. In this game, everything anyone ever wanted to be can be done. Deceive others and make sure that they don't know which way you flop on the three pole picket fence. What's the best way to deceive my enemies and then spring a trap on them. Become creative! It'll be well worth it in the long run.
 
