{RIF YOU HAVE A QUESTION OR AREN'T SURE ABOUT A SITUATION, CONTACT AN IMMORTAL.{z

Some situations that have popped up:

---
Player {BA{z attacks Player {RB{z, but Player {RB{z wins and kills his attacker.
Player {RB{z then later attacks and kills Player {BA{z. This is {MNOT MULTIKILL{z,
because Player {BA{z instigated the first fight, where player {RB{z instigated
the second.
