Player {BA{z attacks and kills Player {RB{z. Player {RB{z then groups with
Player {YC{z. Player {BA{z attacks Player {YC{z, and Player {RB{z autoassists;
Player {BA{z kills Player {RB{z (and perhaps even Player {YC{z). This is {MNOT
MULTIKILL{z, for a couple of reasons; 1, Player {BA{z didn't attack Player {RB{z,
