0 10 sentinel relationships~
A listing of the various relationships with the various clans. Those clans not
mentioned are considered neutral, and therefore, are treated as an individual basis.
 
Ruler - While their intentions are good, their laws tend to get in the way from
making the right choices. As a general rule, being friends with them is a good idea,
and while acting according to their regulations while under their nose is oftentimes 
the best course of actions, it's not difficult to convince them to deputize the
members of Sentinel to have the ability to legally break the laws. If WANTED, the
best course of action is escape. Do NOT attack the Ruler clan hall in retaliation.
 
Knight - Although they tend to look down their noses at us, they can be useful
allies. They, also, can be misguided, and when they have such an episode, it is best
to simply avoid them.
 
Scion - Kill them upon sight. Or lack thereof.
 
Shadow - Twist them to suit our purposes whenever possible. But be prepared to
take them out when necessary.
 
Barbarian, Chaos, Sylvan, Warlock - Individual case-by-case basis.
However, try not to cause interior termoil inside those clans. We do not wish to
see the clans themselves fall apart simply because you're the root of spats
between members. Everyone suffers, then, and that is something Sentinel doesn't
want.
