halfings are fleet of foot, and easy to miss, although not very strong. 
They typically look just like humans, although they tend to have slightly
exaggerated facial features.  They are prone to exaggerated emotional states
and emotional outbursts, whether happy, sad, hungry, or sleepy.  Once one is
set in his ways, it's very difficult to change his mind.  
