0 0 'HALF-ORCS' HALFORCS~
Half-Orcs typically lead one of three lives.  The first choice is to live
amongst humans and be constantly degraded due to being considered ugly,
stupid, and dangerous to be around.  The second is to live amongst orcs, and
to be degraded due to being weak, not as ugly.  The third is to live
solitarily, void of racial companionship.  
Half-Orcs typically look like humans, except taller, broader-shouldered,
and brutish-looking, with pronounced bone structure in the face, as well
as visible tusks protruding from their mouths.
